Name: UCSB
Description: A great university located off the california coast!!

Name: Downtown Oceanside
Description: A small beach town slowly being taken over by beige resorts

Name: Henry Cowell State Park
Description: This is a beautiful old growth redwood forest in upstate California.

Name: Solvang
Description: A danish style town near UCSB with many wineries and kitschy gift shops.

Name: Julian
Description: Julian is a tiny mountain town with one main street and a very good pie shop, located perfect daytrip distance from downtown Oceanside.

Name: Bryce National Park
Description: This national park has many great hiking trails to experience huge canyons and rock formations.
